{"tid":2192071,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"解放軍國際軍事賽連環「蝦碌」","createTime":"2020-09-07T01:30:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-07T14:21:22.000Z","uid":25558,"like":127,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":80,"replies":[{"pid":"4e446f7e964769417f92871623fff6eee62b21a4","tid":2192071,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T01:30:19.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20200907/NO3V5TDBPZEDPERYPK527XG4TM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200907%2FNO3V5TDBPZEDPERYPK527XG4TM%2F&d=YmBpLFXYotmGfWLbQLkNp%2BoeOpwBOZOods3%2BbOb6780%3D&h=d40b7438\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200907%2FNO3V5TDBPZEDPERYPK527XG4TM%2F&h=42325ecb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20200907/NO3V5TDBPZEDPERYPK527XG4TM/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n解放軍國際軍事賽連環「蝦碌」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n中國解放軍在本年度的「國際軍事比賽」獲得亞軍，但連環爆出「蝦碌」事件，包括坦克兵慶祝取得佳績時，高舉調轉的五星旗；炮手甫落坦克即突然暈倒，要戰友拖走治理，讓人汗顏。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/mkjsz_SlzIsJvrU2u-h5krZSBZQ=/2484x1476/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/JIAGJAWPMJEH5LHSOWZJNO5H54.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fmkjsz_SlzIsJvrU2u-h5krZSBZQ%3D%2F2484x1476%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FJIAGJAWPMJEH5LHSOWZJNO5H54.jpg&h=4803578d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■解放軍疑因比賽表現不俗，太興奮而調轉五星旗。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n炮手「暈車浪」<br />\n<br />\n「國際軍事比賽」由俄羅斯主辦，上月23日舉行。參賽國包括俄羅斯、中國、阿塞拜疆、哈薩克等十多個國家。比賽先進行坦克競技，考驗坦克在不同地形的操控通過能力、射擊精準度等。中國去年在此項目表現不濟，三甲不入，錄得參賽以來最差成績。今年，內地不少軍事迷對。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n至8月30日，殺入準決賽的中國坦克兵又再爆「瘀事」。當時，中國的703號坦克正與白羅斯、阿塞拜疆、塞爾維亞等爭入決賽，。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n過程還被直播出街，令人對強調「來之能戰、戰之必勝」的解放軍有不良印象。不過疑似「暈車浪」中國坦克組最終仍奪亞而歸。台灣《自由時報》<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/HAFNRuLdAUP2FKSrFIFSIpbRLIU=/1575x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/U2I2Q2BVVRA67KFLJ2IHGGTPUA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FHAFNRuLdAUP2FKSrFIFSIpbRLIU%3D%2F1575x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FU2I2Q2BVVRA67KFLJ2IHGGTPUA.jpg&h=49a2de24&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■參賽解放軍炮手暈倒，被拖離現場。"},{"pid":"f67983d88ef3f35a9c3fd7d80aba3dd040d43475","tid":2192071,"uid":73340,"like":292,"dislike":1,"score":291,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T01:31:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jseeA6L.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjseeA6L.gif&h=a6ab536e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"614ea7db5e05195458b4023f5f658b8ff32069b5","tid":2192071,"uid":297997,"like":65,"dislike":3,"score":62,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T01:31:25.000Z","msg":"比曬錢都係第二"},{"pid":"c11cbeab3315f16db54ca95bec5f88e25f7dd4f0","tid":2192071,"uid":228955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T01:32:06.000Z","msg":"On9"},{"pid":"41255a51c1fcd862b38c139d938497b54dc113ed","tid":2192071,"uid":116466,"like":43,"dislike":1,"score":42,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T01:35:13.000Z","msg":"解放軍疑因比賽表現不俗，<br />\n太興奮而[red]調轉五星旗<br />\n<br />\n手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f23b06b8263ad489f950f78bdba333d607919514","tid":2192071,"uid":116466,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T01:35:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>解放軍疑因比賽表現不俗，<br />\n太興奮而<span class=\"red\">調轉五星旗</span><br />\n<br />\n手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"6cc6346504650f9b8216fa690bbdb4eb8400c518","tid":2192071,"uid":44646,"like":116,"dislike":4,"score":112,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T01:36:30.000Z","msg":"支旗向前展示，後方拍就緊係調轉<br />\n<br />\n個比賽本身都好多地方搞笑<br />\n參賽的都係同俄國友好國家，全部出賽既都係T72車系<br />\n中國出96B，應該係默認96系列抄T72<br />\n<br />\n其他國家都係出現役車，<br />\n唯一例外：96B係解放軍無裝備的車款<br />\n係特別為參賽而改良<br />\n有少少出茅之嫌"},{"pid":"13b2a2827b89972705d46ec3485c17b41e98b584","tid":2192071,"uid":11719,"like":38,"dislike":0,"score":38,"quote":{"pid":"614ea7db5e05195458b4023f5f658b8ff32069b5","tid":2192071,"uid":297997,"like":65,"dislike":3,"score":62,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T01:31:25.000Z","msg":"比曬錢都係第二"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T01:37:16.000Z","msg":"你睇下咩國家參加，個第二根本係造俾強國"},{"pid":"b4d56309529d902a20c59ef128ceb69d61baa714","tid":2192071,"uid":48631,"like":34,"dislike":0,"score":34,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T01:38:03.000Z","msg":"俄羅斯、中國、阿塞拜疆、哈薩克"},{"pid":"0512220e81fb14815cd93e57c64cf50c9c1fc12a","tid":2192071,"uid":85461,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T01:38:11.000Z","msg":"報告班長 第三營第三連"},{"pid":"0c7c0ecce5b8ccb312127ac2010842a58f000848","tid":2192071,"uid":58209,"like":30,"dislike":0,"score":30,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T01:38:53.000Z","msg":"點解我未聽過美英法會參加呢啲比賽<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95f2d782dcba6b15d1d35c7810cb3efcba406be5","tid":2192071,"uid":193476,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T01:40:01.000Z","msg":"呢班兵已經係精英"},{"pid":"b4bdc0ac5bc39a7c0bad83c83554618aef7845ab","tid":2192071,"uid":343017,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T01:40:47.000Z","msg":"國際既標準係咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7434f860f04fda6bd63351db3d52e6049e285aff","tid":2192071,"uid":286792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T01:41:23.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"70c3ff891b9e69785032ce3692a889d13fddcb47","tid":2192071,"uid":34410,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"quote":{"pid":"0c7c0ecce5b8ccb312127ac2010842a58f000848","tid":2192071,"uid":58209,"l